      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required for MRL 2; default level 1 is acceptable.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency mapping between experimental and simulation input parameters is not required at MRL 2. Qualitative correspondence between experimental boundary conditions and simulation inputs was documented in the simulation report."
    }
