    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors met or exceeded the required level for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB applications. The assessment team notes that this model has been applied in clinical research contexts and the results are consistent with independent experimental observations from multiple laboratories.",
